    dc:description "FIGURE 6. Comparisons of (1) dorsal overview, (2) ventral overview, (3) lateral head, (4) dorsal head, and (5) ventral head among A. damingensis sp. nov. (ANU20220009; holotype) (A), A. yangdatongi (KIZ 034327; holotype) (B), A. ningshanensis (ANU 20220002; paratype). Photos of the holotype of A. yangdatongi are obtained from Hou et al. (2021), remaining photos by Dian-Cheng Yang." ;
